-- Kewpie Targets Increasing Overseas Sales to $489 Million, Nikkei Reports
-- B y   K a n a   N i s h i z a w a
-- 2010-10-10T23:49:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-10/kewpie-targets-increasing-overseas-sales-to-489-million-nikkei-reports.html
Kewpie Corp. aims to increase its
overseas sales to 40 billion yen ($489 million) in fiscal 2015,
Nikkei English News reported, without citing anyone. The company
plans to raise the percentage of sales it receives overseas to
10 percent in fiscal 2015 from 3 percent in fiscal 2009, while
targeting demand in China and Islamic countries, Nikkei
reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
